        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Mixo is hosted-only.</strong> Your site stays on Mixo servers permanently.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Value Proposition</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Framer: Design excellence.</strong> Premium aesthetics and performance worth paying for.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Mixo: Smart value.</strong> Professional results at budget prices with maximum ease.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Choose Based on Your Priorities</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Choose Framer (8.8/10) if:</strong> You want the best designs, code export matters, you're design-focused, budget allows $15+/mo.</li>
        <li><strong>Choose Mixo (8.5/10) if:</strong> Budget is $9/mo, you want maximum ease, you need a simple site, free tier matters.</li>
        <li><strong>Framer is better for:</strong> Designers, startups, portfolios, tech companies, modern brands.</li>
        <li><strong>Mixo is better for:</strong> Small business, personal sites, beginners, budget projects, quick launches.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Recommendation -->
    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Recommendation</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Framer for design excellence.</strong> If you want the best designs and can afford $15+/mo.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-4">
        <strong>Mixo for smart value.</strong> If you want professional results at $9/mo with zero learning curve.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Framer delivers the best designs in class. Mixo delivers the best value for most users.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Framer for design excellence. Mixo for budget-friendly value.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/reviews/framer-ai" class="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Read Framer Review â†’
        </a>
