      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Framer worth the extra $6/month?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">If design impacts your revenue: yes. Framer's superior designs convert 7-15% better in my tests. For designers, startups, portfoliosâ€”the $6/mo pays for itself. For simple lead gen or personal sites, Mixo is sufficient.</p>
